doc.previous: Bmi regional also regularly operates holiday charter flights over the summer months These destinations have included Bastia on the island of Corsica on behalf of specialist tour operator Corsican Places from Bristol and Verona from Bristol on behalf of another specialist tour operator Inghams During 2011 bmi regional aircraft operated on behalf of BMI direct flights between London Heathrow and Beja in the Alentejo region of Portugal for Sunvil Discovery 11
doc.after: As of April 2015 the bmi Regional fleet consists of the following aircraft 12
